verse.lines:
Tho’ by sin opprest,
Go to Him for rest;
“Our God is able to deliver thee”

‘Tis the grandest theme
thro’ the ages rung;
‘Tis the grandest theme
for a mortal tongue;

‘Tis the grandest theme
in the earth or main;
‘Tis the grandest theme
for a mortal strain;

‘Tis the grandest theme,
let the tidings roll,
To the guilty heart,
to the sinful soul;
